    def test_edit_decree_name_under_approving(self, decree_3rd_type):
        """
        Проверка редактирования названия приказа при согласовании
        https://tfs.university.innopolis.ru/tfs/DefaultCollection/%D0%92%D0%BD%D1%83%D1%82%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%BD%D1%8F%D1%8F%20%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B7%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B1%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%BA%D0%B0/_workitems/edit/59784
        """
        logger.info("Проверка на стадии Подготовки документа")
        admin_panel.auth_as_user(decree_3rd_type.author)
        decrees_list_page.open_decree_by_number(decree_3rd_type.decree_id)
        decree_page.decree_name.clear().type("тест")
        decree_page.decree_name.should(have.value("тест"))
        decree_page.send_consideration()
    
        logger.info("Проверка на стадии Проверки корректности документа")
        admin_panel.auth_as_user(decree_3rd_type.corrector)
        decrees_list_page.open_decree_by_number(decree_3rd_type.decree_id)
        decree_page.decree_name.clear().type("test")
        decree_page.decree_name.should(have.value("test"))
        decree_page.accept_corrector()
    
        logger.info("Проверка на стадии Согласование первой группой согласующих")
        admin_panel.auth_as_user(decree_3rd_type.supervisors_1st_group[0])
        decrees_list_page.open_decree_by_number(decree_3rd_type.decree_id)
        decree_page.decree_name_inputs.should(be.empty)
>       decree_page.approve_last_supervisor()
